lead_paragraph: Maria Sharapova said she was inspired as well as frustrated after losing to Serena Williams in the Australian Open quarter-finals on Tuesday, a defeat which extended her losing streak against the American to 12 years and 18 matches.

headline.print_headline: Back to the Drawing Board for Inspired, Frustrated Sharapova
